"Narrated Sulaiman Ash-Shaibani:I heard Ash-Shu`bi saying, \"I was told by a man who had passed with the Prophet (ﷺ) by a grave that was separate from the other graves that he (the Prophet (ﷺ) ) led them in the prayer and they prayed behind him.\" I said, \"O Abu `Amr! Who narrated that to you?\" He replied, \"Ibn `Abbas"